WEBVTT

00:02.094 --> 00:03.850
You said we'd help them across.

00:03.875 --> 00:05.208
(Cephalo) And bring a Demon with them?

00:05.260 --> 00:06.643
The hell with that!

00:06.711 --> 00:09.212
I guess my first owners were
pretty eager to unload me.

00:09.264 --> 00:10.680
And who knows about my parents.

00:14.052 --> 00:15.268
(gasping)

00:15.353 --> 00:16.386
(Amberle) I've heard
of place like this.

00:16.471 --> 00:17.969
Buildings from the age of Man.

00:18.723 --> 00:22.058
This is how we find the Bloodfire.

00:22.110 --> 00:23.860
Your father is dead!

00:23.895 --> 00:25.395
(shouting)

00:25.447 --> 00:27.563
(groaning)

00:27.649 --> 00:29.899
No!

00:29.984 --> 00:32.785
Now you are king.

00:32.871 --> 00:33.870
Let's go!

00:33.905 --> 00:35.238
(groaning)

00:35.323 --> 00:36.572
Eretria!

00:36.624 --> 00:37.573
She's out there alone.

00:37.625 --> 00:38.741
(Wil) We'll find her.

00:42.447 --> 00:46.115
♪♪

00:49.537 --> 00:53.122
(whimpering)

00:53.208 --> 00:55.055
My friends will find us.

00:55.377 --> 00:57.117
And you'll be sorry when they do.

00:57.462 --> 00:59.962
Your "friends" took off
and didn't look back.

01:01.883 --> 01:02.359
Stop.

01:09.376 --> 01:10.594
What is this place?

01:11.262 --> 01:12.531
Human settlement.

01:12.846 --> 01:13.789
But how?

01:14.098 --> 01:16.298
This is Troll country.

01:16.350 --> 01:18.217
They'd be slaughtered.

01:18.302 --> 01:19.051
Move.

01:19.136 --> 01:20.719
(man) Okay, let's go.

01:24.558 --> 01:26.642
♪♪

01:26.694 --> 01:29.645
(children laughing)

01:29.697 --> 01:31.813
(sheep bleating)

01:35.219 --> 01:36.652
Any interest in these?

01:36.704 --> 01:37.703
Of course.

01:37.788 --> 01:39.655
The maps, this atlas.

01:39.707 --> 01:40.898
All of the books.

01:43.327 --> 01:43.977
What about her?

01:47.214 --> 01:48.055
Trust me.

01:48.582 --> 01:50.048
You don't want this one.

01:50.134 --> 01:51.898
I'm gonna trade her in Grimpen Ward,

01:53.220 --> 01:53.672
pay off some debts.

01:56.140 --> 01:58.257
She was after this when I found her.

02:00.761 --> 02:02.311
Seemed pretty important.

02:08.235 --> 02:09.484
Okay.

02:09.520 --> 02:10.852
I'll take it.

02:10.937 --> 02:12.604
And I want the girl.

02:12.690 --> 02:13.914
Girl's not for sale.

02:14.775 --> 02:16.858
Okay... I changed my mind.

02:17.945 --> 02:18.938
Put it all back.

02:19.496 --> 02:21.563
Tye, we had a deal.

02:21.782 --> 02:22.656
Not anymore.

02:23.701 --> 02:26.868
Not unless... you sell me the girl.

02:26.920 --> 02:28.170
I'm not for sale!

02:29.673 --> 02:30.602
She'll cost you double.

02:31.592 --> 02:34.320
(groaning)

02:34.845 --> 02:35.794
Sold.

02:35.879 --> 02:36.878
The wound's infected, Tye.

02:36.964 --> 02:38.406
She's worthless if she dies.

02:39.550 --> 02:40.789
Well, then, Frances,

02:41.435 --> 02:42.851
let's get her to the infirmary.

02:43.887 --> 02:45.020
(groaning)

02:45.055 --> 02:46.388
What are you doing?

02:46.440 --> 02:47.578
Let me go.

02:50.778 --> 02:51.943
I need to find my friends.

02:52.029 --> 02:53.979
Shh, relax.

02:54.064 --> 02:55.314
It's gonna be okay.

02:57.067 --> 02:58.483
You're in Utopia now.

02:58.569 --> 03:02.237
♪♪

03:05.492 --> 03:09.411
